      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for the security aspect. Could you go a bit deeper into the economic side? Specifically, I need my students to understand the arguments regarding how strict enforcement affects the labor market and the social safety net. They need to be able to argue the position that uncontrolled immigration prioritizes certain groups at the expense of domestic workers/citizens.",
